    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with primary lumbar herniated disc disease who have received and performed a
             standardized conservative treatment program with intensive exercises.

          -  Oral and written acceptance.

          -  Age 18 and above.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with central or lateral spinal stenosis due to spondylosis or disc
             degeneration who needed bilateral decompression, laminectomy or fusion.

          -  Patients with cauda equina syndrome who needed acute operative treatment.
      </textblock>
